PrecisOrder authorizing (a) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign (i) an AGREEMENT FOR COOPERATION IN THE AREA OF NUCLEAR RESEARCH between Canada and the European Atomic Energy Community, and (ii) an Agreement Amending the AGREEMENT FOR SCIENTIFIC AND TECHNOLOGICAL COOPERATION between Canada and the European Community, done at Halifax on June 17, 1995, or (b) the issuance of an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing other Cabinet Ministers or senior officials to sign them.

precis:
Order authorizing (a) the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs
to sign (i) an AGREEMENT FOR COOPERATION IN THE AREA OF NUCLEAR RESEARCH
between Canada and the European Atomic Energy Community, and (ii) an
Agreement Amending the AGREEMENT FOR SCIENTIFIC AND TECHNOLOGICAL

June 17, 1995, or (b) the issuance of an Instrument of Full Powers
authorizing other Cabinet Ministers or senior officials to sign them.
